<h2>📋 Your Report Status Has Been Updated</h2>

<p>Hello <%= @report.user.email %>,</p>

<p>Great news! The status of your report has been updated:</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1e40af;"><%= @report.title %></h3>
  <p><strong>📍 Location:</strong> <%= @report.address %></p>
  <p><strong>🏘️ Barangay:</strong> <%= @report.barangay.name %></p>
  
  <div style="margin: 15px 0;">
    <p><strong>Status Changed:</strong></p>
    <p>
      <span class="status-badge status-<%= @old_status %>" style="margin-right: 10px;"><%= @old_status.titleize %></span>
      <span style="font-size: 18px;">→</span>
      <span class="status-badge status-<%= @new_status %>" style="margin-left: 10px;"><%= @new_status.titleize %></span>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<% if @new_status == 'resolved' %>
  <p style="background-color: #d1fae5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #10b981;">
    <strong>🎉 Issue Resolved!</strong><br>
    Your report has been marked as resolved. Thank you for helping improve our community!
  </p>
<% elsif @new_status == 'in_progress' %>
  <p style="background-color: #dbeafe; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;">
    <strong>🔧 Work in Progress</strong><br>
    Your report is now being addressed by the barangay officials. They will keep you updated on the progress.
  </p>
<% end %>

<%= link_to "View Report Details", report_url(@report), class: "button" %>

<p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">
  <strong>What's Next?</strong><br>
  • Check the report for any new comments from officials<br>
  • If you have additional information, you can add comments<br>
  • If the issue persists, you can create a follow-up report
</p>
